ikes on Iran]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132264845.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[At a recent summit, President Trump reinforced the United States' unwavering support for Nato, highlighting the strong camaraderie among member nations. Nato's Secretary General Mark Rutte backed the US military actions in Iran, and allies from Europe and Canada committed to boosting their defense budgets while extending aid to Ukraine. The summit concluded with a declaration underscoring collective defense principles and ongoing military support for Ukraine.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/want-to-remain-with-you-trumps-nato-u-turn-as-chief-backs-us-strikes-on-iran/articleshow/132264845.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/want-to-remain-with-you-trumps-nato-u-turn-as-chief-backs-us-strikes-on-iran/articleshow/132264845.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-08T18:52:10+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132264926,imgsize-80026.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Saudi Arabia executes man convicted of luring wife to desert and burning her alive ]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132266427.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/saudi-arabia-executes-man-for-burning-wife-alive-after-luring-her-to-desert/articleshow/132266427.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/saudi-arabia-executes-man-for-burning-wife-alive-after-luring-her-to-desert/articleshow/132266427.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-08T20:24:05+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="htt